amooinc</a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Ottobre 28, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Trust my words, avoid this junk. Save your time. Just needed a simple chart, it will have you go through like DMV style process to make one chart, just to find out there\'s nothing you can unless you pay.  I get that developers need to make money and I\'m willing to spend $$ on good products, but what\'s the point of releasing this plugin if I can\'t even test my own data? What a sad plugin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">works fine, easy to use</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 su 5 stelle\" data-title-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/b2media/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5c44175d8456811d6831eb69db0d3273?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5c44175d8456811d6831eb69db0d3273?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/b2media/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">b2media</a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Settembre 18, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">works fine, easy to use</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works well and devs are responsive.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 su 5 stelle\" data-title-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joshintosh/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/77eeba99883836acac96caf24e1a8ff5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/77eeba99883836acac96caf24e1a8ff5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joshintosh/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Josh <small>(joshintosh)</small></a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Agosto 29, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">We are using it on a rather complicated multisite install. After much research we went with this plugin for our editors needs. Our site is anything but \"out of the box\" and as such, some of edges didn\'t fit. The developers here are great and helpful. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Admin spam everywhere!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 su 5 stelle\" data-title-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/petervandoorn/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ccc687e5dd725b32526a5cec5f369e70?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ccc687e5dd725b32526a5cec5f369e70?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/petervandoorn/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Peter Hardy-vanDoorn <small>(petervandoorn)</small></a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Marzo 31, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Warning, this plugin is one of those obnoxious ones that litter your admin with spam for their other products!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For example, on every single image edit window in the media library there\'s a panel telling me that my image is too large and I should install their plugin to optimise the image. The image is an 8kb svg!!!!!!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>And there\'s a large panel on every single post edit page too. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Utterly unacceptable and obnoxious! The WordPress plugin team really should ban this sort of spammy behaviour!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Paid for pro still display link to them</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 su 5 stelle\" data-title-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wagnerjsilva/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7df6b4dc4cfc6d2ff02762c0c2cbcdd1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7df6b4dc4cfc6d2ff02762c0c2cbcdd1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wagnerjsilva/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">wagnerjsilva</a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Dicembre 7, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Despite paying for a pro version, their graphs continue to display:\n\nChart by Visualizer\n\nThis has been an absolutely appalling take over by the new owners, inserting links into people\'s front end should never have happened in first place, even for free versions.\n\nOffer premium features, and people will pay for it. That was a ransomware, that despite paying for, did not work.\n\nReverting to old version.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Don&#039;t use if you for Google Sheets Functionality</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 su 5 stelle\" data-title-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/magnifier7536/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/55db81c2a8756f69d0e9ae3ae26db83a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/55db81c2a8756f69d0e9ae3ae26db83a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/magnifier7536/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">magnifier7536</a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Settembre 17, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Themeisle purports to support csv URLs from Google Sheets, but this feature has been completely non-functional for all users for months. \n\n- support/topic/cannot-import-11/\n- support/topic/invalid-data-type-error/\n- support/topic/invalid-data-types-error-despite-being-valid/</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works great for my site</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 su 5 stelle\" data-title-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/howardshouse/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4dd3edf7218d6bc912f923f52d8ac384?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4dd3edf7218d6bc912f923f52d8ac384?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/howardshouse/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">howardshouse</a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Giugno 13, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Needed a bit of adjustment, but I\'ve used it for a few sites now with great success</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A pity 5 charts have been removed from the free version</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 su 5 stelle\" data-title-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gjwmvg/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ce49fd9223db94eda199251025778b7a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ce49fd9223db94eda199251025778b7a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gjwmvg/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Guinea Pig <small>(gjwmvg)</small></a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Marzo 17, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I use the plug-in since 2014 ( version 1.4.2.3 ) and made many charts for my non-commercial website because of the easy use and nice charts. I can understand that developping and support costs money but in 2014 the plug-in was free to use (the support then was worse - seems to be the owner did not want to spend any effort and sold his plug-in -).\n\nSince version 3.7.2 five (area, geo, bubble, scatter &amp; column) of the nine free usable charts have been moved behind the paywall. Pity for me because i have many column-charts which are not visible anymore after updating to V3.7.2. I wonder why the column charts have been \"removed\" from the free version. I\'am not able to replace the column-charts with bar-charts (big difference/to much data).\n\nvery very pity</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">not working google spreadsheet</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 su 5 stelle\" data-title-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vermont10/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e63e447692d9a9df852866bc1bed226c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e63e447692d9a9df852866bc1bed226c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vermont10/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">vermont10</a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Febbraio 17, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">not workink import from google spreadsheet csv</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 su 5 stelle\" data-title-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/djrandypanama/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1b814f1c928717b8b755c96074a030d9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1b814f1c928717b8b755c96074a030d9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/djrandypanama/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">djrandypanama</a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Gennaio 15, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great plugin</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:116:\"A simple and powerful WordPress chart plugin to create responsive charts &amp; tables and embed them into your site.\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:7:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:63:\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=3015999\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"Charts Selection\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:63:\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-2.gif?rev=3015999\";s:7:\"cap